Package: BioNERO
Type: Package
Title: Easy and comprehensive biological network reconstruction and analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Fabricio", "Almeida-Silva", email="fabricio_almeidasilva@hotmail.com", role=c("cre", "aut"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5314-2964"))
Description: This package is used to reconstruct biological networks (coexpression, protein-protein interaction and gene regulatory networks) and analyze them. For coexpression networks, several functions are available to automatically preprocess the expression data prior to network reconstruction.
Depends: R (>= 4.0)
License: GPL-3
